response.overview: After the death of her mother, Sara moves to the South Side of Chicago to live with her father and gets transferred to a majority-black school. Her life takes a turn for the better when befriends Chenille and her brother Derek, who helps her with her dancing skills.
response.tagline: The Only Person You Need To Be Is Yourself.
response.title: Save the Last Dance

titles.title: Save the Last Dance - Sei einfach du selbst
